These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
There 5 different types of food: carrot, cucumber, garlic, kale, asparagus
City: hamburg, paris, miami, prague, nizza
House: cottage, victorian, cape-cod, farmhouse, townhouse
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, family, sports, animation
 1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is the person eating asparagus##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the victorian house is the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is the person eating cucumber##1
 7. the cottage house is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person eating kale is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the victorian house is the person watching documentary movies##1
12. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Food         | cucumber  | carrot    | kale | garlic    | asparagus  |
| City   | paris  | hamburg | miami | prague | nizza  |
| House           | cottage     | townhouse     | farmhouse  | victorian   | cape-cod    |
| Movie-Genre         | family | sports    | horror | documentary  | animation |

