.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, orchid, azalea, iris
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, cricket, badminton, rowing, weightlifting
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, lilac, ebony, brown, turquise
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, boat, motorbike, snowmobile, bus
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who growsorchid##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
11. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person who growsorchid is the person who's sport is cricket##1
13. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Flower          | orchid        | iris | daisy     | azalea      | aconite  |
| Sport           | cricket   | badminton | weightlifting    | rowing | golf |
| Color   | ebony | brown     | turquise | black    | lilac  |
| Transport   | snowmobile     | boat | train    | bus      | motorbike    |

