.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, poker, mah-jongg, scrabble
House: farmhouse, wooden, colonial, gothic-revival, ranch-style
There 5 different types of food: papaya, potato, onion, plum, cauliflower
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, february, june, november, august
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 3. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
 5. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
 6. the wooden house is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating potato##1
11. the person eating onion is the farmhouse house##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Game      | mah-jongg          | poker  | canasta       | monopoly     | scrabble      |
| House         | wooden | ranch-style | gothic-revival  | colonial   | farmhouse    |
| Food   | potato        | cauliflower | papaya | plum    | onion   |
| Birthday     | july   | june | august      | february | november |

