City: new-york, hannover, paris, rome, miami
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
10. the owner of the goat is the person who growslily##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
12. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Pet          | hedgehog        | snake       | ferret | bird   | goat  |
| Hobby   | writing | collecting | reading | singing   | dancing |
