There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, american, thai, colombian, british
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, camping, hiking, magic-tricks, chess
 1. the american is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the american##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the nigerian is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the british is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the american##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the thai##1
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Birthday          | january    | november  | june | may    | july      |
| City           | marseilles | rome | nizza  | prague | paris |
| Nationality   | thai           | american      | british      | colombian        | nigerian     |
| Hobby         | camping         | hiking  | card-games   | magic-tricks       | chess  |

