.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, azalea, bellflower, balloon-flower
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, water
5 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, dog, hedgehog, mouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, car, subway, roller, trike
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the roller is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
12. the person driving the roller is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Flower         | azalea  | balloon-flower  | zinnia    | iris | bellflower |
| Beverage   | fanta        | soy-milk  | sprite | juice      | water        |
| Pet   | pony       | hedgehog  | dog   | mouse | lizard     |
| Transport         | trike | roller | subway | car  | helicopter      |

