.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, august, november, june, march
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, zinnia, amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, boat, taxi, van, jet-ski
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, brown, black, mauve
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person who growszinnia is the person driving the van##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday      | may      | august       | march         | june  | november |
| Flower   | zinnia  | amaryllis | daisy | sunflower  | balloon-flower  |
| Transport   | van    | boat    | car        | jet-ski | taxi     |
| Color           | amber | brown      | apricot       | black   | mauve   |

