.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, chinese, italian, french, nigerian
City: london, miami, san-francisco, rome, nizza
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, mauve, blue, yellow, blood-red
House: futuristic, tower, gothic-revival, craftsman, wooden
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the wooden house##1
 3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 4. the nigerian is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the nigerian##1
 7. the chinese is the futuristic house##1
 8. the italian is the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes ebony is the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the craftsman house is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
12. the nigerian is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
13. the french is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Nationality   | chinese      | french | italian  | nigerian    | colombian |
| City   | rome     | nizza     | miami | london      | san-francisco      |
| Color           | blue       | ebony     | mauve     | blood-red     | yellow   |
| House         | futuristic | craftsman | tower  | wooden | gothic-revival   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, fantasy, romance, crime
The people have 5 different jobs:  librarian, engineer, freelancer, designer, bartender
City: liverpool, berlin, hamburg, paris, miami
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, tennis, golf, sailing, rowing
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the bartender is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the engineer##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
12. the freelancer is the person watching crime movies##1
13. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy | crime    | thriller   | romance   | mystery |
| Job   | librarian    | freelancer   | bartender | designer | engineer  |
| City           | berlin     | paris | hamburg   | miami | liverpool   |
| Sport     | tennis  | rowing   | cycling    | sailing   | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, light-blue, lavender, mauve, purple
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, coach, entrepreneur, scientist, lawyer
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, old-henry, baccarat, alhambra, cain
There 5 different types of food: corn, radish, lime, pineapple, avocado
 1. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
 2. the scientist is the person eating corn##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the scientist##1
 4. the security-guard is the cain-smoker##1
 5. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the entrepreneur is the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
11. the security-guard is on the far right##1
12. the lawyer is in the middle##1
13. the siglo-smoker is the person who likes mauve##1
14. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Color      | light-blue | mauve   | lavender    | blue       | purple |
| Job   | entrepreneur           | coach   | lawyer   | scientist       | security-guard  |
| Cigar   | old-henry       | siglo | baccarat | alhambra     | cain   |
| Food     | lime    | radish   | pineapple   | corn | avocado   |

 